 of buried layers is both a highly-correlated\nphenomenon, and a subtle component in the XRR model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jan 2013 21:54:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Nov 2013 20:24:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
