y maximize the energy efficiency. (2) Wireless power\ntransfer can enhance the energy efficiency, especially in the interference\nlimited regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2013 15:53:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-18"}
